.DS_Store
*.log
# SDD runtime lockfiles — local exclusion state, not versionable memory (unlike .engram/)
.sdd/locks/
# Resolved memory mode (ACTIVE|DEGRADED) — reflects THIS machine's engram availability, local runtime state
.sdd/memory-mode
# .sdd/memory-index.jsonl is the deterministic memory index — it MUST travel with the
# repo (like .engram/). Keep it tracked; never add a pattern that ignores it.
!.sdd/memory-index.jsonl
.idea/
.vscode/
open-pr.sh
PR_BODY.md
sdd-protocol-fixes.patch
